---
title: Mediterranean Chicken Salad with Black Olive-Sherry Vinaigrette
description: Aged sherry vinegar is full of nutty, complex intensity. Whisked into a garlicky black olive vinaigrette, it gives this salad both elegance and depth. Creamy butter beans contrast crisp green beans for textural intrigue, while bright parsley and tangy feta add pops of flavor.
